title: #VoxInTheBox! Boudreau/Thielen/Motzko
description: Vox In The Box returns! PA and Nordo are joined in the Xcel Energy Center Press Box by Wild Head Coach Bruce Boudreau to start the show. Adam Thielen stops by to talk Vikings as well as his pond hockey days. The Athletic's Michael Russo talks Florida Panthers and Wild hockey and World Juniors Team USA and St. Cloud State Head Coach Bob Motzko calls in from Buffalo!
